Conflicts: mpt-status
Description: VMware OVF deployment helper
 The VMware OVF deployment helper configure basic system properties like
 hostname, setup an initial root password, generate ssh host keys etc.
 .
 Hostname and IP configuration can be supplied via VMware's OVF environment
 implementation. This requires vmtoolsd in the search path and suitable
 configured vApp options.
